&lt;li&gt;Some exposure to Python or scripting for data manipulation and analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with a BI tool (PowerBI, Looker, Tableau, Superset, Redash, or any other alternative)&lt;/li&gt;
