&lt;li data-start=&quot;643&quot; data-end=&quot;758&quot;&gt;Champion engineering processes and rituals that enable strong collaboration, accountability, and team efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;761&quot; data-end=&quot;892&quot;&gt;Monitor team velocity and capacity to optimize resource allocation, proactively balancing bandwidth against delivery commitments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;895&quot; data-end=&quot;1010&quot;&gt;Coordinate cross-team dependencies and stakeholder alignment to remove bottlenecks and maintain smooth execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1013&quot; data-end=&quot;1186&quot;&gt;Stay hands-on in critical initiatives by guiding design decisions, enforcing sound design patterns, and participating in code reviews to maintain high engineering quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1189&quot; data-end=&quot;1316&quot;&gt;Ensure robust monitoring, alerting, and observability for all owned services, consistently meeting defined SLIs and SLOs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1319&quot; data-end=&quot;1459&quot;&gt;Partner with Product Managers to define, track, and publish post-release product metrics, driving transparency and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
