&lt;li&gt;Build, lead, and scale multiple high-performing engineering teams, including managers and senior individual contributors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strengthen team capacity and capability through proactive mentorship, structured career development, succession planning, and rigorous performance management.&lt;/li&gt;
